snippet.title: Amber Heard's witnesses EXPOSED! Johnny Depp's lawyer turns their own words against them!
snippet.description:
It is now day 14 of the Johnny Depp Vs The Sun trial, and the last day of witnesses on the stand. There were several big spicy moments that happened today, with Amber Heard's sister and her two friends. 

there was also a new video released that really damaged the credibility of Heard's sister.
